sql_statement.static: SELECT P.Name AS `Port Name`,(SELECT ifnull(SUM(TX.FrameCount),0) FROM TxEotStreamResults AS TX WHERE TX.RxPortName=P.NAME)-(SELECT ifnull(SUM(RX.SigFrameCount),0) FROM RxEotStreamResults AS RX WHERE RX.PortName=P.NAME AND RX.IsExpectedPort=1)+(SELECT ifnull(SUM(RX.DuplicateFrameCount),0) FROM RxEotStreamResults AS RX WHERE RX.PortName=P.Name) AS `Rx Signature Packets Lost`,(SELECT ifnull(SUM(RX.SigFrameCount),0) FROM RxEotStreamResults AS RX WHERE RX.PortName=P.Name AND RX.IsExpectedPort=0) AS `Rx Misdirected Packets`,(SELECT ifnull(SUM(RX.DuplicateFrameCount),0) FROM RxEotStreamResults AS RX WHERE RX.PortName=P.Name) AS `Rx Duplicate Packets`,(SELECT ifnull(SUM(RX.SigFrameCount),0) FROM RxEotStreamResults AS RX WHERE RX.PortName=P.Name AND RX.IsExpectedPort=1) AS `Rx Signature Packets`,(SELECT ifnull(SUM(TX.FrameCount),0) FROM TxEotStreamResults AS TX WHERE TX.PortName=P.Name) AS `Tx Signature Packets` FROM Port AS P
SELECT `Port Name`,`Rx Signature Packets Lost`,`Rx Misdirected Packets`,`Rx Duplicate Packets`,`Rx Signature Packets`,`Tx Signature Packets` from StcPacketStats
SELECT * FROM vsw_perf_cfg

SELECT FrameSize, Load, OfferedRate, COALESCE(((Rx.L1BitCount)/(Rx.LastArrivalTime - Rx.FirstArrivalTime))*(SELECT DISTINCT (FixedLoad/MbpsLoad) FROM GeneratorConfig), 0.0) AS ThroughputPercent, COALESCE(((Rx.L1BitCount)/(Rx.LastArrivalTime - Rx.FirstArrivalTime)), 0.0) AS ThroughputMbps, COALESCE(((1e6 * Rx.SigFrameCount)/(Rx.LastArrivalTime - Rx.FirstArrivalTime)), 0.0) AS ThroughputFps, COALESCE(Rx.TotalLatency, 0) AS TotalLatency, Rx.AvgLatency AS AvgLatency, Rx.MinLatency AS MinLatency, Rx.MaxLatency AS MaxLatency, COALESCE(Rx.TotalJitter, 0) AS TotalJitter, Rx.AvgJitter AS AvgJitter, Rx.MinJitter AS MinJitter, Rx.MaxJitter AS MaxJitter, TxFrameCount, COALESCE(Rx.FrameCount, 0) AS RxFrameCount, COALESCE(Rx.DroppedFrameCount, TxFrameCount, 0) AS DroppedFrameCount, COALESCE(100.0 * Rx.DroppedFrameCount/TxFrameCount, 100.0) AS DroppedFramePercent, COALESCE(Rx.OutSeqFrameCount, 0) AS OutSeqFrameCount, COALESCE(Rx.DuplicateFrameCount, 0) AS DuplicateFrameCount, COALESCE(Rx.LateFrameCount, 0) AS LateFrameCount, COALESCE(Rx.L1BitCount, 0) AS BitCount, COALESCE(Rx.FirstArrivalTime, 0) AS FirstTime, COALESCE(Rx.LastArrivalTime, 0) AS LastTime, SbTx.ParentHnd AS ParentHnd, TxPort, COALESCE(Rx.PortName, 'NA') AS RxPort, LossTolerance

FROM (SELECT Sb.Active AS SbActive, CASE WHEN Sb.FrameLengthMode='IMIX' THEN 'imix' ELSE Sb.FixedFrameLength END AS FrameSize, (SELECT DISTINCT FixedLoad FROM GeneratorConfig) AS Load, (Tx.L1BitCount / ((SELECT DISTINCT Duration FROM GeneratorConfig) * 1e6)) * (SELECT DISTINCT FixedLoad/MbpsLoad FROM GeneratorConfig) AS OfferedRate, (SELECT LossTolerance FROM vsw_perf_cfg_iter) AS LossTolerance, COALESCE(Tx.FrameCount, 0) AS TxFrameCount, COALESCE(Tx.PortName, 'NA') AS TxPort, Tx.StreamId, Sb.ParentHnd FROM Streamblock AS Sb LEFT JOIN TxEotStreamResults AS Tx ON Sb.Handle=Tx.ParentStreamBlock) AS SbTx
LEFT JOIN RxEotStreamResults AS Rx ON StreamId=Rx.Comp32 AND (Rx.SigFrameCount IS NULL OR IsExpectedPort) WHERE SbActive

Latency (us)', COALESCE(ROUND(AvgJitter, 3), 'NA') AS 'Avg. Jitter (us)', TxFrameCount AS 'Tx Frame Count', RxFrameCount AS 'Rx Frame Count', DroppedFrameCount AS 'Dropped Frame Count', ROUND(DroppedFramePercent, 2) AS 'Dropped Frame (%)', OutSeqFrameCount AS 'Out of Sequence Frame Count', DuplicateFrameCount AS 'Duplicate Frame Count', LateFrameCount AS 'Late Frame Count', TxPort AS 'Tx Port', RxPort AS 'Rx Port' FROM vsw_pkt_loss

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS vsw_perf_iter_agg (FrameSize INTEGER, Trial INTEGER, Load FLOAT, OfferedRate FLOAT, AvgThroughputPercent FLOAT, AvgThroughputMbps FLOAT, AvgThroughputFps INTEGER, MinThroughputPercent FLOAT, MaxThroughputPercent FLOAT, TotalLatency INTEGER, AvgLatency FLOAT, MinLatency FLOAT, MaxLatency FLOAT, TotalJitter INTEGER, AvgJitter FLOAT, MinJitter FLOAT, MaxJitter FLOAT, TxFrameCount INTEGER, RxFrameCount INTEGER, DroppedFrameCount INTEGER, DroppedFramePercent FLOAT, OutSeqFrameCount INTEGER, DuplicateFrameCount INTEGER, LateFrameCount INTEGER, FloodedFrameCount INTEGER)

SELECT DISTINCT FrameSize, NULL AS Trial, Load, AVG(OfferedRate) AS OfferedRate, SUM(ThroughputPercent)/(SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT DISTINCT TxPort FROM vsw_pkt_loss)) AS AvgThroughputPercent, SUM(ThroughputMbps)/(SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT DISTINCT TxPort FROM vsw_pkt_loss)) AS AvgThroughputMbps, SUM(ThroughputFps)/(SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT DISTINCT TxPort FROM vsw_pkt_loss)) AS AvgThroughputFps, MIN(ThroughputPercent) AS MinThroughputPercent, MAX(ThroughputPercent) AS MaxThroughputPercent, SUM(TotalLatency) AS TotalLatency, 0.01 * SUM(TotalLatency)/SUM(RxFrameCount) AS AvgLatency, MIN(MinLatency) AS MinLatency, MAX(MaxLatency) AS MaxLatency, SUM(TotalJitter) AS TotalJitter, 0.01 * SUM(TotalJitter) / SUM(RxFrameCount) AS AvgJitter, MIN(MinJitter) AS MinJitter, MAX(MaxJitter) AS MaxJitter, SUM(TxFrameCount) AS TxFrameCount, SUM(RxFrameCount) AS RxFrameCount, SUM(DroppedFrameCount) AS DroppedFrameCount, COALESCE(100.0 * SUM(DroppedFrameCount) / SUM(TxFrameCount), 0.0) AS DroppedFramePercent, SUM(OutSeqFrameCount) AS OutSeqFrameCount, SUM(DuplicateFrameCount) AS DuplicateFrameCount, SUM(LateFrameCount) AS LateFrameCount, CASE WHEN (SELECT SUM(SigFrameCount) FROM AnalyzerPortResults)>=SUM(RxFrameCount-DuplicateFrameCount) THEN (SELECT SUM(SigFrameCount) FROM AnalyzerPortResults)-SUM(RxFrameCount-DuplicateFrameCount) ELSE 0 END AS FloodedFrameCount FROM vsw_pkt_loss
UPDATE vsw_perf_iter_agg SET Trial=
(SELECT TrialNum FROM vsw_perf_cfg) WHERE Trial IS NULL

Latency (us)', COALESCE(ROUND(MaxLatency, 3), 'NA') AS 'Max. Latency (us)', COALESCE(ROUND(AvgJitter, 3), 'NA') AS 'Avg. Jitter (us)', COALESCE(ROUND(MinJitter, 3), 'NA') AS 'Min. Jitter (us)', COALESCE(ROUND(MaxJitter, 3), 'NA') AS 'Max. Jitter (us)', TxFrameCount AS 'Tx Frame Count', RxFrameCount AS 'Rx Frame Count', DroppedFrameCount AS 'Dropped Frame Count', ROUND(DroppedFramePercent, 2) AS 'Dropped Frame (%)', OutSeqFrameCount AS 'Out of Sequence Frame Count', DuplicateFrameCount AS 'Duplicate Frame Count', LateFrameCount AS 'Late Frame Count', FloodedFrameCount AS 'Flooded Frame Count' FROM vsw_perf_iter_agg ORDER BY rowid DESC LIMIT 1

sql_statement.static: CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS vsw_iter_tmp (IsConverged INTEGER, ConvergedVal FLOAT, CurrVal FLOAT, MaxVal FLOAT, MbpsFactor FLOAT, FpsFactor FLOAT)
DELETE FROM vsw_iter_tmp

SELECT DISTINCT IsConverged, CAST(ConvergedVal AS FLOAT) AS ConvergedVal, CAST(CurrVal AS FLOAT) AS CurrVal, MaxVal, Gc.MbpsLoad/Gc.FixedLoad AS MbpsFactor, Gc.FpsLoad/Gc.FixedLoad AS FpsFactor FROM spirent_methodology_RateIteratorCommand AS Ic JOIN RelationTable AS Rt ON Ic.Handle=Rt.SourceHnd JOIN Tag ON Rt.TargetHnd=Tag.Handle, GeneratorConfig AS Gc JOIN Generator AS Gn ON Gn.Handle=Gc.ParentHnd WHERE Tag.Name='RateIter' AND Gn.ParentHnd IN (SELECT DISTINCT ParentHnd FROM StreamBlock)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS vsw_perf_iter (FrameSize INTEGER, Trial INTEGER, ConfigRate FLOAT, ConfigRateMbps FLOAT, ConfigRateFps FLOAT, OfferedRate FLOAT, OfferedRateMbps FLOAT, OfferedRateFps FLOAT, AvgThroughputPercent FLOAT, AvgThroughputMbps FLOAT, AvgThroughputFps FLOAT, MinThroughputPercent FLOAT, MaxThroughputPercent FLOAT, TotalLatency INTEGER, AvgLatency FLOAT, MinLatency FLOAT, MaxLatency FLOAT, TotalJitter INTEGER, AvgJitter FLOAT, MinJitter FLOAT, MaxJitter FLOAT, TxFrameCount INTEGER, RxFrameCount INTEGER, DroppedFrameCount INTEGER, DroppedFramePercent FLOAT, OutSeqFrameCount INTEGER, DuplicateFrameCount INTEGER, LateFrameCount INTEGER, FloodedFrameCount INTEGER, MaxRate FLOAT, IsConverged INTEGER, ConvergedVal FLOAT)

SELECT DISTINCT FrameSize, Ag.Trial AS Trial, Load AS ConfigRate, ROUND(Load*MbpsFactor,3) AS ConfigRateMbps, ROUND(Load*FpsFactor,3) AS ConfigRateFps, OfferedRate, ROUND(OfferedRate*MbpsFactor,3) AS OfferedRateMbps, ROUND(OfferedRate*FpsFactor,3) AS OfferedRateFps, ROUND(AvgThroughputPercent,3) AS AvgThroughputPercent, ROUND(AvgThroughputMbps,3) AS AvgThroughputMbps, ROUND(AvgThroughputFps,3) AS AvgThroughputFps, ROUND(MinThroughputPercent,3) AS MinThroughputPercent, ROUND(MaxThroughputPercent,3) AS MaxThroughputPercent, TotalLatency, ROUND(AvgLatency,3) AS AvgLatency, ROUND(MinLatency,3) AS MinLatency, ROUND(MaxLatency,3) AS MaxLatency, TotalJitter, ROUND(AvgJitter,3) AS AvgJitter, ROUND(MinJitter,3) AS MinJitter, ROUND(MaxJitter,3) AS MaxJitter, TxFrameCount, RxFrameCount, DroppedFrameCount, DroppedFramePercent, OutSeqFrameCount, DuplicateFrameCount, LateFrameCount, FloodedFrameCount, Ic.MaxVal AS MaxRate, Ic.IsConverged, Ic.ConvergedVal
FROM vsw_perf_iter_agg AS Ag JOIN vsw_perf_cfg AS Cf ON CfgFrameSize=FrameSize AND Trial=TrialNum, vsw_iter_tmp AS Ic
WHERE Ag.Load=(CASE WHEN Ic.IsConverged THEN Ic.ConvergedVal ELSE Ic.CurrVal END)

sql_statement.static: CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS vsw_perf_summ (FrameSize INTEGER, ConfigRate FLOAT, ConfigRateMbps FLOAT, ConfigRateFps FLOAT, OfferedRate FLOAT, OfferedRateMbps FLOAT, OfferedRateFps FLOAT, AvgThroughputPercent FLOAT, MinThroughputPercent FLOAT, MaxThroughputPercent FLOAT, AvgThroughputMbps FLOAT, MinThroughputMbps FLOAT, MaxThroughputMbps FLOAT, AvgThroughputFps FLOAT, MinThroughputFps FLOAT, MaxThroughputFps FLOAT, AvgLatency FLOAT, MinLatency FLOAT, MaxLatency FLOAT, AvgJitter FLOAT, MinJitter FLOAT, MaxJitter FLOAT, TxFrameCount INTEGER, RxFrameCount INTEGER, DroppedFrameCount INTEGER, DroppedFramePercent FLOAT, OutSeqFrameCount INTEGER, DuplicateFrameCount INTEGER, LateFrameCount INTEGER, FloodedFrameCount INTEGER, MaxRate FLOAT, MaxRateMbps FLOAT, MaxRateFps FLOAT, IsConverged INTEGER, ConvergedVal FLOAT)

SELECT DISTINCT COALESCE(FrameSize, (SELECT CfgFrameSize FROM vsw_perf_cfg)) AS FrameSize, ConfigRate, ConfigRateMbps, ConfigRateFps, OfferedRate, OfferedRateMbps, OfferedRateFps, AVG(AvgThroughputPercent) AS AvgThroughputPercent, MIN(AvgThroughputPercent) AS MinThroughputPercent, MAX(AvgThroughputPercent) AS MaxThroughputPercent, AVG(AvgThroughputMbps) AS AvgThroughputMbps, MIN(AvgThroughputMbps) AS MinThroughputMbps, MAX(AvgThroughputMbps) AS MaxThroughputMbps, AVG(AvgThroughputFps) AS AvgThroughputFps, MIN(AvgThroughputFps) AS MinThroughputFps, MAX(AvgThroughputFps) AS MaxThroughputFps, 0.01 * SUM(TotalLatency) / SUM(RxFrameCount) AS AvgLatency, MIN(MinLatency) AS MinLatency, MAX(MaxLatency) AS MaxLatency, 0.01 * SUM(TotalJitter) / SUM(RxFrameCount) AS AvgJitter, MIN(MinJitter) AS MinJitter, MAX(MaxJitter) AS MaxJitter, SUM(TxFrameCount) AS TxFrameCount, COALESCE(SUM(RxFrameCount), (SELECT SUM(RxFrameCount) FROM vsw_perf_iter)) AS RxFrameCount, COALESCE(SUM(DroppedFrameCount), (SELECT SUM(DroppedFrameCount) FROM vsw_perf_iter)) AS DroppedFrameCount, COALESCE(100.0 * SUM(DroppedFrameCount) / SUM(TxFrameCount), 100.0) AS DroppedFramePercent, COALESCE(SUM(OutSeqFrameCount), (SELECT SUM(OutSeqFrameCount) FROM vsw_perf_iter)) AS OutSeqFrameCount, COALESCE(SUM(DuplicateFrameCount), (SELECT SUM(DuplicateFrameCount) FROM vsw_perf_iter)) AS DuplicateFrameCount, COALESCE(SUM(LateFrameCount), (SELECT SUM(LateFrameCount) FROM vsw_perf_iter)) AS LateFrameCount, COALESCE(SUM(FloodedFrameCount), (SELECT SUM(FloodedFrameCount) FROM vsw_perf_iter)) AS FloodedFrameCount, COALESCE(MaxRate, (SELECT MaxRate FROM vsw_perf_iter)) AS MaxRate, (10000.0 * ConfigRateMbps) / (ConfigRate * MaxRate) AS MaxRateMbps, (10000.0 * ConfigRateFps) / (ConfigRate * MaxRate) AS MaxRateFps, SUM(IsConverged)>0 AS IsConverged, ConvergedVal FROM vsw_perf_iter AS It JOIN vsw_perf_cfg ON FrameSize=CfgFrameSize
